      <trans-unit id="8513029167698384448" datatype="html">
        <source>Sobre o SIGA</source>
        <target>About SIGA</target>
        <context-group purpose="location">
          <context context-type="sourcefile">src/app/pages/public/about/about.html</context>
          <context context-type="linenumber">14,16</context>
        </context-group>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="6530395672904771361" datatype="html">
        <source> Uma plataforma criada para apoiar organizações de proteção animal de forma mais simples, organizada e humana. </source>
        <target> A platform created to support animal welfare organizations in a simpler, more organized and humane way. </target>
        <context-group purpose="location">
          <context context-type="sourcefile">src/app/pages/public/about/about.html</context>
          <context context-type="linenumber">17,18</context>
        </context-group>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="7404309311984318906" datatype="html">
        <source> O SIGA surge da necessidade de melhorar a forma como muitas organizações gerem informação sobre animais, adotantes e processos de adoção. A proposta passa por reunir tudo num único sistema claro, intuitivo e estruturado. </source>
        <target> SIGA arises from the need to improve how many organizations manage information about animals, adopters and adoption processes. The proposal is to gather everything in a single clear, intuitive and structured system. </target>
        <context-group purpose="location">
          <context context-type="sourcefile">src/app/pages/public/about/about.html</context>
          <context context-type="linenumber">22,24</context>
        </context-group>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="6990443002155929174" datatype="html">
        <source>Origem</source>
        <target>Origin</target>
        <context-group purpose="location">
          <context context-type="sourcefile">src/app/pages/public/about/about.html</context>
          <context context-type="linenumber">34,35</context>
        </context-group>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="3039953517660565917" datatype="html">
        <source>Porque nasceu este projeto</source>
        <target>Why this project was born</target>
        <context-group purpose="location">
          <context context-type="sourcefile">src/app/pages/public/about/about.html</context>
          <context context-type="linenumber">35,37</context>
        </context-group>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="6547151409286692488" datatype="html">
        <source> Em muitas organizações, a informação encontra-se dispersa por folhas de cálculo, mensagens, documentos ou apontamentos soltos. Isso dificulta o acompanhamento do historial dos animais, o controlo dos processos de adoção e a consulta rápida de dados importantes no dia a dia. </source>
        <target> In many organizations, information is scattered across spreadsheets, messages, documents, or loose notes. This makes it difficult to track animal histories, control adoption processes, and quickly access important data in daily operations. </target>
        <context-group purpose="location">
          <context context-type="sourcefile">src/app/pages/public/about/about.html</context>
          <context context-type="linenumber">41,44</context>
        </context-group>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="1923606360098846795" datatype="html">
        <source> O SIGA foi pensado precisamente para responder a esse problema, oferecendo uma plataforma que ajuda a centralizar informação e a tornar a gestão mais clara, consistente e acessível. </source>
        <target> SIGA was designed precisely to address this issue, offering a platform that helps centralize information and make management clearer, more consistent, and accessible. </target>
        <context-group purpose="location">
          <context context-type="sourcefile">src/app/pages/public/about/about.html</context>
          <context context-type="linenumber">48,50</context>
        </context-group>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="366604124396966672" datatype="html">
        <source>Objetivo</source>
        <target>Objective</target>
        <context-group purpose="location">
          <context context-type="sourcefile">src/app/pages/public/about/about.html</context>
          <context context-type="linenumber">60,61</context>
        </context-group>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="8321998720764992370" datatype="html">
        <source>O que o SIGA pretende oferecer</source>
        <target>What SIGA aims to offer</target>
        <context-group purpose="location">
          <context context-type="sourcefile">src/app/pages/public/about/about.html</context>
          <context context-type="linenumber">61,63</context>
        </context-group>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="4037436607245216517" datatype="html">
        <source> O objetivo da plataforma é apoiar o registo e acompanhamento dos animais, facilitar a organização dos processos de adoção e melhorar a forma como a informação é consultada dentro de cada organização. </source>
        <target> The objective of the platform is to support the registration and monitoring of animals, facilitate the organization of adoption processes, and improve the way information is accessed within each organization. </target>
        <context-group purpose="location">
          <context context-type="sourcefile">src/app/pages/public/about/about.html</context>
          <context context-type="linenumber">66,68</context>
        </context-group>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="560008961080146352" datatype="html">
        <source> Mais do que guardar dados, o SIGA procura ajudar as organizações a trabalhar com mais estrutura, reduzir a desorganização e ter uma visão mais completa sobre cada caso. </source>
        <target> More than just storing data, SIGA aims to help organizations work with more structure, reduce disorganization, and have a more complete view of each case. </target>
        <context-group purpose="location">
          <context context-type="sourcefile">src/app/pages/public/about/about.html</context>
          <context context-type="linenumber">72,74</context>
        </context-group>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="4962332592922082992" datatype="html">
        <source>Visão</source>
        <target>Vision</target>
        <context-group purpose="location">
          <context context-type="sourcefile">src/app/pages/public/about/about.html</context>
          <context context-type="linenumber">84,85</context>
        </context-group>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="3528056969017991906" datatype="html">
        <source> Uma ferramenta pensada para a realidade das organizações </source>
        <target> A tool designed for the reality of organizations </target>
        <context-group purpose="location">
          <context context-type="sourcefile">src/app/pages/public/about/about.html</context>
          <context context-type="linenumber">86,87</context>
        </context-group>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="2804895148723269600" datatype="html">
        <source> Esta plataforma foi idealizada tendo em conta necessidades concretas observadas em contextos reais. A intenção é desenvolver uma solução útil, prática e adaptada ao trabalho diário de associações e organizações que lidam com acolhimento, acompanhamento e adoção responsável de animais. </source>
        <target> This platform was designed considering the concrete needs observed in real contexts. The intention is to develop a useful, practical, and adapted solution for the daily work of associations and organizations dealing with animal care, monitoring, and responsible adoption. </target>
        <context-group purpose="location">
          <context context-type="sourcefile">src/app/pages/public/about/about.html</context>
          <context context-type="linenumber">92,95</context>
        </context-group>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="224081177712017758" datatype="html">
        <source> O foco está na simplicidade, na clareza da informação e na criação de uma base sólida que possa evoluir no futuro com novas funcionalidades. </source>
        <target> The focus is on simplicity, clarity of information, and the creation of a solid foundation that can evolve in the future with new features. </target>
        <context-group purpose="location">
          <context context-type="sourcefile">src/app/pages/public/about/about.html</context>
          <context context-type="linenumber">99,100</context>
        </context-group>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="1288578523830865013" datatype="html">
        <source>Evolução</source>
        <target>Evolution</target>
        <context-group purpose="location">
          <context context-type="sourcefile">src/app/pages/public/about/about.html</context>
          <context context-type="linenumber">110,111</context>
        </context-group>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="2815389994370983855" datatype="html">
        <source>Um projeto em crescimento</source>
        <target>A growing project</target>
        <context-group purpose="location">
          <context context-type="sourcefile">src/app/pages/public/about/about.html</context>
          <context context-type="linenumber">111,113</context>
        </context-group>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="6661439306449312042" datatype="html">
        <source> O SIGA pretende continuar a evoluir, acompanhando as necessidades das organizações e melhorando progressivamente a experiência de utilização. A visão é construir uma plataforma cada vez mais útil, capaz de apoiar uma gestão animal mais responsável, organizada e eficiente. </source>
        <target> SIGA aims to continue evolving, keeping up with the needs of organizations and progressively improving the user experience. The vision is to build a platform that becomes increasingly useful, capable of supporting more responsible, organized, and efficient animal management. </target>
        <context-group purpose="location">
          <context context-type="sourcefile">src/app/pages/public/about/about.html</context>
          <context context-type="linenumber">116,119</context>
        </context-group>
      </trans-unit>
